notes: Replay of match rained out on 26th February.

PA Strang 9.4-1-21-5, best ever bowling by a Zimbabwean in ODIs (previous best: AIC Lock 5-44 v NZ 03/02/1996), 1st 5 wicket haul in the World Cup since CJ McDermott 04/11/1987 (AUS v PAK 5-44), 5th all-time best bowling by any player in the World Cup (best since KH MacLeay 6-39, AUS v IND 13/06/1983), equal 31st best bowling in the history of ODIs.
AC Waller and GW Flower 59 1st wicket partnership, 6th highest for Zimbabwe in ODIs.

milestones.description: Chudasama and Otieno's 53-run partnership is KENYA's highest for the 2nd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 24 between Otieno and Steve Tikolo
Odumbe and Tito Odumbe's 42-run partnership is KENYA's highest for the 6th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 19 between Thomas Odoyo and Tito Odumbe
This is the highest match aggregate (271) involving teams Zimbabwe & Kenya in ODIs
Rajab Ali has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (4) for KENYA, going past Chudasama
